    • Constructor Detail

      • SparqlQueryResultDataSource

        public SparqlQueryResultDataSource(URL endpoint,
                                   String queryVariables,
                                   String queryBody)
        Creates a data source from answers to a remote SPARQL query.
        Parameters:
        endpoint - web location of the resource the query will be evaluated on
        queryVariables - comma-separated list of SPARQL variable names (without leading ? or $)
        queryBody - content of the WHERE clause in the SPARQL query

      • SparqlQueryResultDataSource

        public SparqlQueryResultDataSource(URL endpoint,
                                   LinkedHashSet<Variable> queryVariables,
                                   String queryBody)
        Creates a data source from answers to a remote SPARQL query.
        Parameters:
        endpoint - the web location of the resource the query will be evaluated on.
        queryVariables - the variables of the query, in the given order. The variable at each position in the ordered set will be mapped to its correspondent query answer term at the same position.
        queryBody - the content of the WHERE clause in the SPARQL query. Must not contain newline characters ("\n").
